title: Shiv Sena workers storm Mumbai BCCI office to protest Indo-Pak cricket meet - newsR
text: The Shiv Sena workers stormed into the BCCI office to protest against the meeting with the Pakistan Cricket board to discuss the India-Pakistan bilateral series slated for December. The Shiv Sainiks charged into the office chanting 'vande matram' and slogans against PCB chief Shahryar Khan. Â»
